{"type":"message","id":"7191a846","parentId":"47d58f70","timestamp":"2026-04-27T15:04:37.345Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gmail has no new emails in the last hour. iCloud has 3 emails - let me check if any are new/unread.\n\niCloud emails:\n- ID 8: Re: Looking for new apartment from RC Leasing, today (2026-04-27 12:20 UTC = 8:20 AM ET) - this is new\n- ID 7: Re: Looking for new apartment from RC Leasing, 2026-04-13 - marked R (read)\n- ID 6: Re: Apartment Inquiry from Taylor Alexander, 2026-01-22 - marked R (read)\n\nSo ID 8 is new/unread. Let me read it to get more details.","thinkingSignature":"fb467d0476329ceb6f45cae987bbe2e9176a938a11e27e001448c640ec7815ec"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zq6ymbvo9per_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"himalaya message read 8 --account icloud 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":918,"output":187,"cacheRead":19036,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20141,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777302272605,"responseId":"063eae0019c30a37b8d6eb34cce3fbd6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c2d1d984","parentId":"7191a846","timestamp":"2026-04-27T15:04:38.197Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_zq6ymbvo9per_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[2m2026-04-27T15:04:37.933700Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T15:04:37.933802Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T15:04:37.933817Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T15:04:37.933858Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\nFrom: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Saturday, April 25, 2026 1:49 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHi Amy, I wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part o\nReport This Email<removed-link>\n\n\nHi Amy,\n\n\n\nI wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part of the application on his end.\n\n\n\nWe are still very interested in a 1 bedroom / 1 bathroom unit. Please let me know if you need anything else from me in the meantime, or if there are any updates on availability.\n\n\n\nThank you,\n\nRobert Galletta\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/Outlook-A picture .png\"><#/part>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":844,"aggregated":"[2m2026-04-27T15:04:37.933700Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T15:04:37.933802Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T15:04:37.933817Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T15:04:37.933858Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\nFrom: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Saturday, April 25, 2026 1:49 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHi Amy, I wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part o\nReport This Email<removed-link>\n\n\nHi Amy,\n\n\n\nI wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part of the application on his end.\n\n\n\nWe are still very interested in a 1 bedroom / 1 bathroom unit. Please let me know if you need anything else from me in the meantime, or if there are any updates on availability.\n\n\n\nThank you,\n\nRobert Galletta\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/Outlook-A picture .png\"><#/part>","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777302278197}}
